_sText:
The map is based on the word "virtual". The Ts and the CTs fight they may go along the bottom path or go up the ramp or go left or right. There was no basic theme just the colour, green and red.

Map Details:
There are 48 CT spawns.
There are 48 T spawns.
There is one secret.

How To Extract:
Unzip and extract both files in the zip folder into "cstrike/maps".
